Made by BruceLee



Requires:
=========

ImageMagick:
	sudo apt-get install imagemagick
Screenlets:
	sudo apt-get install screenlets
NowPlaying screenlet (>= v.0.3.3.3 improved by BruceLee):
	http://www.gnome-look.org/content/show.php?content=136480



	
Installation:
=============

Copy the folder "Border_Fade-200px" to "~/.screenlets/NowPlaying/themes/"

